    Given an empty graph
    And having executed:
      """
      CREATE (a:A)
      CREATE (b1:B {num: 0}), (b2:B {num: 1})
      CREATE (c1:C), (c2:C)
      CREATE (a)-[:REL]->(b1),
             (a)-[:REL]->(b2),
             (b1)-[:REL]->(c1),
             (b2)-[:REL]->(c2)
      """
    When executing query:
      """
      MATCH (a:A)-[ab]->(b:B)-[bc]->(c:C)
